     <text:p text:style-name="P41"><text:bookmark text:name="user-content-fn-6 Copy 1"/><text:soft-page-break/>Ad revenue shifts and integration. <text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#user-content-fnref-6" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link">↩</text:a></text:p>
