     <text:p text:style-name="P41"><text:bookmark text:name="user-content-fn-7 Copy 1"/>Infrastructure timelines. <text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#user-content-fnref-7" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link">↩</text:a></text:p>
