   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T10">15. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">McKinsey Global Institute. (2016). Bridging Global Infrastructure Gaps. Estimates annual global infrastructure investment and sectoral allocation.</text:span></text:p>
